erlang: erlang Concurrent/Distributed programming language.
erlang:
erlang: Erlang is a  general purpose programming language  and RT enviroment.
erlang: It  has  built-in support  for  concurrency,  distribution and  fault
erlang: tolerance. It is used in several large telecommunication systems from
erlang: Ericsson, and  is best suited  for distributed, reliable  and/or soft
erlang: real-time concurrent systems.
erlang:
erlang: This packages includes OTP (the "standard library" of Erlang).
erlang:
erlang: Make sure to read www.erlang.org for more information.
